[DQR.IFRS.0129.9603] It is expected that TreasuryShares with a value of 142,000 reported in the network role http://naturhouse.com/xbrl/2021/roles/EstadoDeSituacionFinancieraResumen should be equal to the dimensionally qualified concept, Equity with the dimension ifrs-full:ComponentsOfEquityAxis = ifrs-full:TreasurySharesMember and a reported value of 142,000 multiplied by -1.
